 20→// Explicit alias map for clustering emergent category variants.
 21→// Targets don't need to be in CANONICAL_PATTERN_CATEGORIES —
 22→// this clusters semantically-equivalent novel categories together.
 23→// Insert alias lookup runs AFTER exact canonical match but BEFORE Levenshtein,
